==制作==
[[File:Barack_Obama,_Steve_Martin,_Jim_Parsons,_DreamWorks_Animation,_2013.jpg|thumb]][[奥巴马|奥巴马]]赴梦工厂公司参观，会见电影配音[[吉姆·帕森斯|吉姆·帕森斯]]和[[史提夫·馬丁|史提夫·馬丁]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Johnson|first=Ted|title=Obama Tours DreamWorks Animation, Visits With Steve Martin and Jim Parsons|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/obama-tours-dreamworks-animation-visits-with-steve-martin-and-jim-parsons-1200887780/|accessdate=February 8, 2014|newspaper=Variety|date=November 26, 2013|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402222113/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/obama-tours-dreamworks-animation-visits-with-steve-martin-and-jim-parsons-1200887780/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。]]
2008年，梦工厂宣布以儿童小说《斯麦克节的真正意义》为故事蓝本制作动画电影，并于2011年被原著作者亚当·雷克斯确认<ref>{{cite news|last=Herreras|first=Mari|title=T Q&A Adam Rex|url=http://www.tucsonweekly.com/tucson/t-qanda/Content?oid=2219158|accessdate=February 2, 2012|newspaper=Tucson Weekly|date=September 23, 2010|archive-date=2016-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160621052807/http://www.tucsonweekly.com/tucson/t-qanda/Content?oid=2219158|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rex|first=Adam|title=@delzey Yes, Dreamworks optioned SMEKDAY 3 yrs. ago, and renewed the option this year. If they make it I expect it'll be CGI. #kidlitchat|url=https://www.twitter.com/#!/MrAdamRex/statuses/136632623945629700|work=MrAdamRex|publisher=Twitter|accessdate=February 2, 2012|date=November 16, 2011|archive-date=2011-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110224005300/http://twitter.com/#!/MrAdamRex/statuses/136632623945629700|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年6月20日，片名正式确定为《快乐的斯麦克节》，计划于2014年第四季度上映<ref name=ComingSoonRihanna>{{cite web|title=Jim Parsons and Rihanna to Voice DreamWorks Animation's Happy Smekday!|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=91699|work=DreamWorks Animation|publisher=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=June 20, 2012|date=June 20, 2012|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006135803/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=91699|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年9月，20世纪福克斯公司和梦工厂宣布将于2014年11月26日上映<ref name=Slate2016>{{cite news|title=New Distributor Twentieth Century Fox Unveils DreamWorks Animation's Release Slate Through 2016|url=http://ir.dreamworksanimation.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=705761|accessdate=September 10, 2012|newspaper=DreamWorks Animation|date=September 9, 2012|author=DreamWorks Animation|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://archive.is/20131012035253/http://ir.dreamworksanimation.com/releasedetail.cfm?ReleaseID=705761|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年6月片名更改为《疯狂外星人》<ref>{{cite web|title=Movie Title Changes|url=http://boxofficemojo.com/schedule/?view=titlechanges&p=.htm|publisher=Box Office Mojo|accessdate=June 16, 2013|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811230859/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/schedule/?view=titlechanges&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年10月，[[史提夫·馬丁|史提夫·馬丁]]和[[珍妮弗·洛佩兹|珍妮弗·洛佩兹]]正式加入该片配音团队<ref name=PRNewswireMartinLopez />。2014年5月20日推迟上映日期，延迟至2015年3月27日上映，而原上映档期被让给了梦工厂的另一部动画电影《[[马达加斯加的企鹅|马达加斯加的企鹅]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/the-penguins-of-madagascar-release-date-home-dreamworks-animation/ |title=DreamWorks Animation Moves Up 'Penguins Of Madagascar' Bow, Bumps 'Home' To 2015 |publisher=Deadline.com |date=2014-05-20 |accessdate=2014-05-20 |archive-date=2014-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140521062705/http://www.deadline.com/2014/05/the-penguins-of-madagascar-release-date-home-dreamworks-animation/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

